It is a Java based Tetris game with Traingular shape pieces. It is equipped with adjustable speed, scoring factor and piece sizes which make it user friendly for old and low vision players also. It is developed only using Java 2D graphics which makes it very efficient in terms of resource consumption.

Language : Java

Project Name: Triangular Tetris

Developer: Varun Kumar Reddy Bankiti

Version : 1.0

Instructions to run:
	Compile and run Tetris.java
		javac Tetris.java
		java Tetris

Requirements: 

	Java Development Kit-7
